M1 — Execution Domain Models & Database Migration
Status: DONE
Started: 2026-04-11
Completed: 2026-04-11
Notes: Delivered:
  - libs/contracts/models.py — 6 new ORM models (Order, OrderFill, Position,
    ExecutionEvent, KillSwitchEvent, ReconciliationReport). Order has 5 check
    constraints, unique client_order_id, FKs to deployments/strategies with
    RESTRICT, relationships to fills/execution_events with uselist=True and
    cascade="all, delete-orphan". All decimal columns use String(50) for
    precision safety. ULID(26) primary keys throughout.
  - migrations/versions/20260411_0009_add_execution_tables.py — Alembic revision
    0009 (depends on 0008). Creates 6 tables with 17 indexes covering
    deployment_id, strategy_id, symbol, correlation_id, status, scope, target_id.
    Check constraints match DB-level enums in libs/contracts/enums.py.
    Downgrade drops in reverse dependency order.
  - libs/contracts/enums.py — Extended with 8 DB-level execution enums
    (OrderSideDB, OrderTypeDB, TimeInForceDB, OrderStatusDB, ExecutionModeDB,
    DeploymentStateDB, KillSwitchScopeDB, ReconciliationStatusDB,
    EmergencyPostureTypeDB).
  - tests/unit/test_execution_models.py — 32 tests: table existence (6),
    Order model (6 incl. relationships, unique constraint, nullable fields),
    OrderFill (2 incl. cascade delete), Position (2 incl. defaults),
    ExecutionEvent (2 incl. cascade delete), KillSwitchEvent (2 incl. MTTH),
    ReconciliationReport (2 incl. discrepancies JSON), check constraint DDL (3),
    migration chain (2), indexes (4), model exports (1).
  - Bug fix: SQLAlchemy 2.0 with __allow_unmapped__=True + `: Any` type
    annotations overrides uselist=True → removed `: Any` from relationship
    attributes to get correct collection behaviour.
  Quality gate: 32/32 new tests pass, 1319/1327 backend tests pass
  (8 pre-existing failures), 1171/1171 frontend tests pass, coverage 83.65%.

M2 — Deployment State Machine & Policy Gates
Status: DONE
Started: 2026-04-11
Completed: 2026-04-11
Notes: Delivered:
  - libs/contracts/deployment.py — Deployment state machine schemas:
    DeploymentState enum (10 states), EmergencyPostureType enum (4 postures),
    DEPLOYMENT_TRANSITIONS map (authoritative transition rules),
    is_valid_transition() helper, DeploymentCreateRequest (frozen, model_validator
    for execution_mode/posture validation), RiskLimits (4 fields with defaults),
    DeploymentTransitionRecord, DeploymentHealthResponse, DeploymentResponse.
  - libs/contracts/errors.py — Added StateTransitionError with current_state
    and attempted_state attributes for clear error reporting.
  - libs/contracts/interfaces/deployment_service_interface.py — 9 abstract
    methods: create_deployment, submit_for_approval, approve_deployment,
    activate_deployment, freeze_deployment, unfreeze_deployment,
    deactivate_deployment, rollback_deployment, get_deployment, get_deployment_health.
  - libs/contracts/interfaces/deployment_repository_interface.py — 5 abstract
    methods: create, get_by_id, update_state, record_transition, list_transitions.
  - libs/contracts/mocks/mock_deployment_repository.py — In-memory mock with
    seed() for test setup and introspection helpers.
  - services/api/services/deployment_service.py — Full state machine implementation.
    Core _transition() method validates against DEPLOYMENT_TRANSITIONS, updates state,
    records audit trail. Pre-activation gates enforce emergency posture (spec rule 6).
    Two-step transitions for activate (approved→activating→active) and deactivate
    (active/frozen→deactivating→deactivated). Structured logging on every transition.
  - services/api/repositories/sql_deployment_repository.py — SQL implementation
    with _deployment_to_dict() and _transition_to_dict() converters.
  - libs/contracts/models.py — Extended Deployment model with state machine columns
    (state, execution_mode, emergency_posture, risk_limits JSON, custom_posture_config
    JSON) + 3 new check constraints. Added DeploymentTransition audit trail model.
  - migrations/versions/20260411_0010_add_deployment_state_machine.py — Alembic
    revision 0010 (depends on 0009). Adds 5 columns to deployments, creates
    deployment_transitions table with indexes.
  - services/api/routes/deployments.py — 10 endpoints: POST /paper, /live-limited,
    /{id}/submit-for-approval, /{id}/approve, /{id}/activate, /{id}/freeze,
    /{id}/unfreeze, /{id}/deactivate, /{id}/rollback, GET /{id}, GET /{id}/health.
    Request-scoped DI. Maps domain errors to HTTP 404/409/422.
  - tests/unit/test_deployment_contracts.py — 41 tests (enum stability, transition
    map exhaustiveness, is_valid_transition, schema validation, RiskLimits bounds,
    frozen models, StateTransitionError).
  - tests/unit/test_deployment_service.py — 31 tests (create, submit, approve,
    activate with gates, freeze, unfreeze, deactivate, rollback, get, health,
    full lifecycle integration, invalid transitions, not-found).
  Quality gate: 72/72 new tests pass, 1391/1399 backend tests pass
  (8 pre-existing failures), 1171/1171 frontend tests pass, coverage 82.91%.

